    • doSearchAndExportResults

      public void doSearchAndExportResults​(SearchParameter mySp)
      Performs the search of degenerated primers. The results are sent to a file. The file name and path are defined in mySp.
      Parameters:
      mySp - contains all the parameters for the search.
      See Also:
      SearchParameter

    • doSearch

      public FASDPD.ResultOfSearch doSearch​(SearchParameter mySp)
      Performs the search of degenerated primers. The file name and path are defined in mySp.
      Parameters:
      mySp - contains all the parameters for the search.
      Returns:
      a ResultOfSearch that contains the designed primers.
      See Also:
      SearchParameter

    • exportDistributionProfile

      public void exportDistributionProfile​(java.lang.String outfile, java.util.List<sequences.dna.Primer> list, int lastPos)
      Exports a distribution profile of primers to a text file, and also exports a simple script to view the profile with gnu-plot.
      Parameters:
      outfile - is the path to the output file
      list - is the List or Primers to export
      lastPos - is the number of the last position of the alignment used to design the primers. Is required for drawing purposes.
